==重要性==
在2006年每秒自转716次的[[PSR_J1748-2446ad|PSR J1748-2446ad]]被发现之前，PSR B1937+21一直保持自转最快中子星的头衔<ref name="j1748">{{cite journal | author = Hessels, J. W. T.; Ransom, S. M.; Stairs, I. H.; Freire, P. C. C.; Kaspi, V. M.; Camilo, F. | title = A Radio Pulsar Spinning at 716 Hz | journal = Science | volume = 311 | year = 2006 | pages = 1901–1904 | url = http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/311/5769/1901 | doi = 10.1126/science.1123430 | pmid = 16410486 | accessdate = 2010-02-14 | issue = 5769 | archive-date = 2008-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080719181702/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/311/5769/1901 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。直至2010年，PSR B19371+21依然是已知自转第二快的中子星<ref name="atnf_list">{{cite web | title = The ATNF Pulsar Database | url = http://www.atnf.csiro.au/research/pulsar/psrcat/proc_form.php?Name=Name&P0=P0&P1=P1&startUserDefined=true&c1_val=&c2_val=&c3_val=&c4_val=&sort_attr=p0&sort_order=asc&condition=&pulsar_names=&ephemeris=short&coords_unit=raj%2Fdecj&radius=&coords_1=&coords_2=&style=Long+with+last+digit+error&no_value=*&fsize=3&x_axis=&x_scale=linear&y_axis=&y_scale=linear&state=query&table_bottom.x=74&table_bottom.y=20 | accessdate = 2009-05-17 | archive-date = 2014-01-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106210908/http://www.atnf.csiro.au/research/pulsar/psrcat/proc_form.php?Name=Name&P0=P0&P1=P1&startUserDefined=true&c1_val=&c2_val=&c3_val=&c4_val=&sort_attr=p0&sort_order=asc&condition=&pulsar_names=&ephemeris=short&coords_unit=raj%2Fdecj&radius=&coords_1=&coords_2=&style=Long+with+last+digit+error&no_value=*&fsize=3&x_axis=&x_scale=linear&y_axis=&y_scale=linear&state=query&table_bottom.x=74&table_bottom.y=20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。这个结果是建立在观测的敏感脉冲周期比发现PSR B1937+21时增大20倍，磁场范围增大100倍的基础上<ref name="backer_remarks">{{cite conference
| first = Don
| last = Backer
| authorlink = Don Backer
| title = Concluding Remarks
| booktitle = Millisecond Pulsars: A Decade of Surprise
| pages = 435–438
| publisher = Astronomical Society of the Pacific
| date = January 3–7, 1994
| location = San Francisco
| accessdate = 2010-02-14
| url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1995ASPC...72..435B}}</ref>。

做为第一颗被发现的[[毫秒脉冲星|毫秒脉冲星]]，PSR B1937+21为探究脉冲星、中子星，甚至是解决[[重力波_(相对论)|引力波]]问题提供了新的“[[实验室|实验室]]”<ref name="encounters">{{cite journal | author = Thomsen, D. E. | title = Pulsar Encounters of a Third Kind | journal = Science News | volume = 123 | page = 4 | url = http://www.jstor.org/stable/3967824 | accessdate = 2010-02-14 | issue = 1 | date = January 1984 | archive-date = 2019-04-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190428163105/https://www.jstor.org/stable/3967824 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。例如，毫秒脉冲星快速旋转所需要的高[[密度|密度]]和[[原子核|原子核]]密度相近，通过观测可以知道在如此高密度条件下物质的活动情况<ref name="j1748"/>。最初发现PSR B1937+21时估计的高减慢率也让人疑惑，因为这意味着[[引力波天文学#引力波探测器|引力波探测器]]可以直接探测到它发出的信号，但实际上信号强度却低于探测器的敏感性。现在普遍接受的观点是每100万年PSR B1937+21的旋转周期频率改变1.5 Hz<ref name="brief_backer_review">{{cite journal | last = Backer | first = Don | authorlink = Don Backer | title = The 1.5 Millisecond Pulsar | journal = Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences | volume = 422 | pages = 180–181 | year = 1984 | url = http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/journal/119527609/abstract | doi = 10.1111/j.1749-6632.1984.tb23351.x | accessdate = 2010-02-14 | issue = Eleventh Texas Symposium on Relativistic Astrophysics | author =  | archive-url = https://archive.today/20130105083556/http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/journal/119527609/abstract | archive-date = 2013-01-05 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。 这种稳定性可以和现在最好的[[原子钟|原子钟]]相媲美，因此可以用来当做建立星历的一种工具<ref name="brief_backer_review"/>。

PSR B1937+21的发现促使世界各大无线电观测站对脉冲星进行广泛的调查，以寻找被遗漏的脉冲星，从而重新振兴了当时被很多人认为已经“垂死的”脉冲星天文学<ref name="kulkarni_overview" />。

